•	Skip Logic (Show/hide questions based on responses)
•	Branching & Conditional Routing
•	Randomization (Question/option shuffling to reduce bias)
•	Piping (Dynamic text insertion from previous answers)
•	Loop & Merge (Repeating blocks for similar questions)


