1. User Management

1.1 User Registration
•	Self-Registration: Users can sign up via email, phone number, or social media (Google, Facebook, LinkedIn).
•	Admin-Managed Registration: Administrators can manually create and approve user accounts.
•	Email Verification: Mandatory email confirmation for self-registered users.
•	CAPTCHA/Security: Spam protection during registration.

1.2 Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) System
•	Predefined Roles:
o	Super Admin: Full system access.
o	Admin: Manages users, questionnaires, and data.
o	Survey Creator: Designs and deploys surveys.
o	Respondent: Only participates in surveys.
•	Custom Roles: Ability to create and assign custom roles with granular permissions.
•	Hierarchy-Based Access: Role inheritance for structured permissions.


1.3 Detailed Profile Management
•	User Profiles:
o	Personal details (name, contact, organization).
o	Profile picture upload.
o	Custom fields (job title, department, etc.).
•	Profile Updates: Users can edit their details.
•	Admin Override: Admins can modify user profiles.
•	Activity Logs: Track profile changes.

2. Questionnaire Programming

2.1 Drag & Drop Feature for All Available Question Types
•	Standard Question Types:
o	Single Selection (Radio Buttons)
o	Multiple Selection (Checkboxes)
o	Dropdown Menu
o	Text Input (Short & Long Answer)
o	Rating Scales (Likert, Star Rating, NPS)
o	Slider Scale
o	Ranking (Drag & Drop Sorting)
o	Matrix Questions (Grid-based)
o	File Upload
o	Date/Time Picker
•	Advanced Question Types:
o	Image Choice
o	Signature Capture
o	Geolocation
o	Audio/Video Response

2.2 Advanced Logic Features
•	Display Logic: Show/hide questions based on previous answers.
•	Skip Logic: Skip to a specific question/section based on conditions.
•	Branching Logic: Redirect respondents based on responses.
•	Piping Logic: Carry forward answers into subsequent questions.
•	Looping & Randomization: Repeat question blocks or randomize question order.
•	Calculated Fields: Auto-compute values based on responses.

2.3 Pre-Built Questionnaire Templates
•	Survey Types:
o	Customer Satisfaction (CSAT)
o	Employee Engagement
o	Market Research
o	Academic Research
o	Event Feedback
o	Product Evaluation
o	Net Promoter Score (NPS)
o	Exit Interviews
o	Psychometric Tests
•	Customizable Templates: Ability to modify and save templates.

2.4 Multi-Language Support
•	Supported Languages: English, Spanish, French, German, Chinese, Arabic, Japanese, Portuguese, Russian, Hindi.
•	Language Toggle: Respondents can switch languages mid-survey.
•	Auto-Translation API: Integration with Google Translate or DeepL.
•	Manual Translation Override: Admin can edit translations.

2.5 Import & Export of Questionnaires
•	Import Formats:
o	CSV/Excel
o	JSON
o	Survey Interchange Formats (QSF – Qualtrics, DOCX – Decipher)
•	Export Formats:
o	PDF (Printable)
o	Word/Excel
o	JSON/XML for API integration
o	QSF (Qualtrics-compatible)

