3.1 Multiple Survey Distribution Channels
•	Email Surveys: Bulk email invites with tracking.
•	Web Links: Shareable public/private URLs.
•	Embedded Surveys: IFrame or JavaScript embed for websites.
•	Social Media Sharing: Direct posting to Facebook, LinkedIn, Twitter.
•	SMS Surveys: Integration with SMS gateways.
