•	API Integration: For automated distribution.

3.2 Gamification Features
•	Points & Badges: Reward respondents for completing surveys.
•	Progress Bars: Visual completion tracking.
•	Leader boards: Top respondents ranking.
•	Instant Rewards: Coupons, vouchers, or certificates.
•	Interactive Elements: Quizzes, puzzles, and animations.

3.3 Responsive Website
•	Mobile-First Design: Works on all devices (iOS, Android, tablets).
•	Cross-Browser Compatibility: Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge.
•	Offline Mode: Save responses when offline, sync later.

