•	Content Management: Facilitate the creation, editing, and publishing of marketing content (images, videos, articles, social media posts).
•	Scheduling: Schedule campaigns to run at specific times or dates.
•	Performance Tracking: Track campaign performance with key metrics (impressions, clicks, conversions, ROI).

3.2 Collaboration and Communication
