•	Lead Nurturing: Tools for nurturing leads through targeted communication and automated follow-ups.
•	Lead Scoring: Assign scores to leads based on engagement and potential conversion.

3.5 Integration and Automation
•	Third-Party Integration: Integrate with tools like CRM systems, email marketing software, and social media platforms.
•	Workflow Automation: Automate repetitive tasks such as email campaigns, social media posting, and lead nurturing.

3.6 Reporting and Analytics
•	Data Visualization: Provide visual representations of marketing data (charts, graphs, dashboards).
•	Performance Analytics: Analyse campaign performance and track KPIs.
•	Customizable Reporting: Generate customized reports based on specific metrics.

3.7 Training and Resources
